  <h2 style="border-top: 1px solid #bc204b;font-family: 'Source Sans Pro', sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 28px;font-weight: normal; color: rgb(188, 32, 75); margin-top:10px; "><img src="http://i.imgur.com/VcDe7rC.png" height=22px width=22px/>&nbsp;&nbsp;OUR STORY</span></h2>
<img src="http://i.imgur.com/5U1DpKD.png" title="HelpMEwell timeline"/>
<p><span style="font-family: 'Source Sans Pro', sans-serif;">Our passion for this project and Family-View comes from the loss of Bruno's sister Pam three years ago due to complications from heart failure. Her death was avoidable. If Family-View and HelpMEwell had existed, alerting Bruno, and Pam's doctor of her complications at home, they would have been able to provide interventions, and she would be alive today.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-family: 'Source Sans Pro', sans-serif;">We've been working on this for several years now, and we deeply believe that we can help keep your parent healthier and more independent. We've talked with a lot of seniors and their families as we've developed the HelpMEwell system, and the number one message that comes across is autonomy. Your parents want to be independent. So staying on top of their health is paramount. It's our mission to help them.</span></p>      
      
